statements: SELECT * FROM partnership;
SELECT partnership_id, partnership_description FROM partnership;
SELECT partnership_start_date, partnership_end_date FROM partnership;
SELECT * FROM partnership WHERE partnership_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM partnership ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM partnership
SELECT partnership_description, partnership_start_date, partnership_end_date FROM partnership ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC
SELECT partnership_id, partnership_description FROM partnership WHERE philanthropic_entity_id = 1 AND partnership_end_date > '2022-01-01'
SELECT * FROM partnership WHERE government_agency_id = 5 ORDER BY partnership_end_date ASC, partnership_start_date DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_partnerships FROM partnership
SELECT * FROM PhilanthropicEntities;
SELECT entity_id, entity_name FROM PhilanthropicEntities WHERE entity_type = 'NPO';
SELECT entity_name, entity_type FROM PhilanthropicEntities ORDER BY entity_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM PhilanthropicEntities WHERE entity_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT entity_name AS Name, entity_type AS Type FROM PhilanthropicEntities;
SELECT * FROM PhilanthropicEntities WHERE entity_type = 'Non-Profit' ORDER BY entity_name DESC;
SELECT entity_name, entity_type FROM PhilanthropicEntities WHERE entity_id IN (1, 3, 5);

SELECT entity_name, agency_name FROM PhilanthropicEntities JOIN GovernmentAgencies ON PhilanthropicEntities.entity_id = GovernmentAgencies.agency_id WHERE PhilanthropicEntities.entity_type = 'Foundation';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS TotalEntities, entity_type FROM PhilanthropicEntities GROUP BY entity_type;
SELECT DISTINCT entity_type FROM PhilanthropicEntities ORDER BY entity_type ASC;
SELECT * FROM philanthropic_entities;
SELECT entity_name, contact_person FROM philanthropic_entities WHERE entity_id = 1;
SELECT agency_name, agency_type, contact_person FROM government_agencies WHERE agency_id = 2;
SELECT entity_name, partnership_description FROM philanthropic_entities WHERE entity_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM partnerships WHERE partnership_status = 'Active';
SELECT * FROM philanthropic_entities
SELECT entity_id, entity_name, contact_person FROM philanthropic_entities WHERE entity_id < 10
SELECT entity_id, entity_name, partnership_description FROM philanthropic_entities WHERE partnership_description IS NOT NULL
SELECT * FROM government_agencies WHERE agency_type = 'Governmental'
SELECT agency_id, agency_name, contact_person FROM government_agencies ORDER BY agency_name DESC
SELECT * FROM Partnerships;
SELECT partnership_id, partnership_type, partnership_start_date FROM Partnerships ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;
SELECT entity_name, entity_type FROM PhilanthropicEntities WHERE entity_type = 'Foundation';
SELECT agency_name, agency_location FROM GovernmentAgencies WHERE agency_type = 'Government';
SELECT partnership_id, detail_description, detail_amount FROM PartnershipDetails WHERE detail_amount > 1000 ORDER BY detail_amount DESC;
SELECT * FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_type = 'Public-Private Partnership';
SELECT partnership_id, partnership_type, partnership_start_date FROM Partnerships ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;

SELECT pd.detail_id, pd.detail_description, p.partnership_type, p.partnership_start_date FROM PartnershipDetails pd INNER JOIN Partnerships p ON pd.partnership_id = p.partnership_id WHERE pd.detail_amount > 10000;
SELECT pa.agency_name, pa.agency_location, pe.entity_name FROM GovernmentAgencies pa INNER JOIN PhilanthropicEntities pe ON pa.agency_id = pe.entity_id;
SELECT p.*, pd.* FROM Partnerships p INNER JOIN PartnershipDetails pd ON p.partnership_id = pd.partnership_id WHERE pd.detail_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM philanthropic_entities;
SELECT entity_name, entity_type FROM philanthropic_entities;
SELECT agency_id, agency_name, location FROM government_agencies;
SELECT partnership_id, partnership_date, partnership_type FROM partnerships;
SELECT funding_id, funding_amount, funding_date FROM partnership_funding;
SELECT * FROM philanthropic_entities;
SELECT entity_name, registration_date FROM philanthropic_entities WHERE entity_type = 'Organization';
SELECT agency_name, location FROM government_agencies ORDER BY agency_name DESC;
SELECT entity_name, agency_name, partnership_date FROM philanthropic_entities JOIN partnerships ON philanthropic_entities.entity_id = partnerships.entity_id ORDER BY partnership_date LIMIT 5;

SELECT entity_name, agency_name, funding_amount FROM philanthropic_entities JOIN partnerships ON philanthropic_entities.entity_id = partnerships.entity_id JOIN partnership_funding ON partnerships.partnership_id = partnership_funding.partnership_id WHERE funding_amount > 10000 ORDER BY funding_amount DESC;
